<section id="welcome" class="bg-base-light text-base-dark dark:bg-base-dark dark:text-gray-50 w-full lg:max-w-[700px]"> 
  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold dark:text-milk-light text-base-dark">Welcome to the Rogue Media Lab</h2>
  <hr class="my-4 w-full dark:border-white border-base-dark">
  <div class="grow max-h-[450px] overflow-y-auto">
    <%= image_tag "RogueMediaLab-banner.png", alt: "Rogue Media Lab", class: "mb-2" %>
    <p class="mb-4 pr-1">
    This is my digital workshop. A place where curiosity meets code. I'm Mason Roberts, the builder behind the lab. By day, I am an automotive technician with over 20 years of experience, training teams and keeping vehicles running with precision. By night, I switch gears to become a designer and developer, crafting the tools and projects I've always wanted.
