    This site is a multipurpose hub. For visitors and potential clients, it is a showcase of active projects, like my automotive maintenance app, the passion-project music player Zuke, and the long-dreamed Hermit Plus. It is also a growing library of development resources and the home base for my Substack and Patreon.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-4 pr-1">
    Take a look around my workbench. Whether you're here to browse, learn, or partner on a project, I've designed this space to be as functional as it is personal. Don't hesitate to reach out if you have any questions.
    </p>
  </div>
</section